title: Lost on You
lastfmSummary: "Lost on You" is a song by American singer and songwriter LP (Laura Pergolizzi), released as the lead single from her 2016 album Lost on You. Known for her distinctive voice and emotionally raw songwriting, LP's "Lost on You" became a breakout hit, showcasing her unique blend of pop, folk, and rock influences. The song garnered widespread attention for its heartfelt lyrics, captivating melody, and LP's powerful vocal performance.
